tips
====================

task
---------------------
    task add pacman due:eow recur:weekly

edit video
---------------------
* change to mp3:

        ffmpeg -i 1.flv -f mp3 -ab 192000 -vn music.mp3
* merge mkv:

        mkvmerge -o out.mkv -A video.mp4 music.mp3

git
---------------------
* rm tag:

        git tag -d 0.2 0.3
        git push origin :refs/tags/{0.2,0.3}

X
---------------------
* Xephyr:

        Xephyr :1 -screen 800x600
        export DISPLAY=:1.0
        wm &

